S.FORM: Tjailjaking i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Tjailjaking. u kasalumaluma' nu Tjailjaking sa, 240 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 875 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 820 ku tademaw, pakalatu 94 . u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 55 ku tademaw, pakalatu 6 . u kasabinacadan, Paiwan 84 , Rukai 2 , Bunun 1 , Puyuma 1 , zumazuma 5 . malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan
